唔到<br />\n兩敗俱傷</span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"98c6b8254d3dc1f37634197400cac4760508a9bc","tid":1936453,"uid":321709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a37d79e11c5d9e60c1ff7fef013f0a109964ea1","tid":1936453,"uid":54371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T12:43:26.000Z","msg":"好，不過記住玩初選"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T04:28:25.000Z","msg":"唔該支持聯署，用選民壓力逼候選人「埋枱」參加初選/協調！<br />\n<br />\n【重開行動Post】立會要初選， 「三不投」聯署<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1935886\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1935886</a>"},{"pid":"7afa156d8c55c83b3822c4f6ec6e3ea3032c2e32","tid":1936453,"uid":321709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6369586974381508f41b6badb772a9fd0d89ad0a","tid":1936453,"uid":37396,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T10:01:28.000Z","msg":"無所謂，總之肯參加初選就得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T04:28:37.000Z","msg":"唔該支持聯署，用選民壓力逼候選人「埋枱」參加初選/協調！<br />\n<br />\n【重開行動Post】立會要初選， 「三不投」聯署<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1935886\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1935886</a>"},{"pid":"99d4a3f2c245b5d76072a1250570efb676b3c8f1","tid":1936453,"uid":321709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1dadac5612df97941165d1b7740fb502ac09e048","tid":1936453,"uid":62226,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2162049dd25acc3ce990c76e92b65ec3cd2b8459","tid":1936453,"uid":13503,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T08:43:59.000Z","msg":"真心唔建議知名度低素人參戰"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T09:25:34.000Z","msg":"如果一堆人肯組成一張名單又唔同講法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如王百羽本身四年前都有份喺青政+天民台名單排名單第二名參選"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T04:29:16.000Z","msg":"唔該支持聯署，用選民壓力逼候選人「埋枱」參加初選/協調！<br />\n<br />\n【重開行動Post】立會要初選， 「三不投」聯署<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1935886\" data-auto